  help             Shows this message.
  joined           Says when a member joined.
  invite           Returns a Link to the Invite URL for this bot
  source           Returns a link to the source code for this bot

Type ;help command for more info on a command.
You can also type ;help category for more info on a category.

24 Sep 2017 20:40:38 : The Pack, bot-chat, Ayana#8911, ```css
[Music Help]

=music (j)oin - Join your current voice channel
=music (p)lay [Song] - Play and or enqueue a song/playlist
   [--voice <Channel>] - Specify the voice channel to connect to
   [--text <Channel>] - Specify the text channel to bind to
   [--region <Region>] - Force connection to specified region

=music (q)ueue [Song] - Show Queue or Enqueue song/playlist
   [--next] - Enqueue song/playlist next
   [--pos <Position>] - Enqueue song/playlist to specified position

=music purge (pg) - Remove all items from the queue
=music (d)elete <Number|Search> - Delete one or more items from the queue

=music (s)kip - Skip/Remove item in position 1 of queue
=music shuffle (sf) - Shuffle queue
=music (r)epeat <on|one|off> - Manage queue repeat

=music providers (pv) - Shows a list of available providers

=music (l)eave - Leaves the voice channel

Examples:
    =music p example song
    =music p example song --next --text bot-commands
    =music j --voice music --text commands
    =music q example song --pos 10
    =music sf
    =music d example song
    =music r one

<> = required information, [] = optional information, | = or, do not include <> [] or | in your command input
Please join the support server for any questions. (=support for link)```
